test_all_one_range:
assert [81, 83, 85] == [1, 1, 1, 1]
  At index 0 diff: 81 != 1
  Right contains one more item: 1
  Full diff:
  - [1, 1, 1, 1]
  + [81, 83, 85]
test_even_range:
assert [81, 83, 85] == []
  Left contains 3 more items, first extra item: 81
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [81, 83, 85]
test_odd_same_number:
assert [81, 83, 85] == [-11, -11, -11, -11]
  At index 0 diff: 81 != -11
  Right contains one more item: -11
  Full diff:
  - [-11, -11, -11, -11]
  + [81, 83, 85]
